   ``I reached the point where I wanted to say something besides,
`Run like hell.''' _ Anita Collins of the U.S. Department of
Agriculture's research office, explaining that one motivation for
studying ways to repel ``killer bees'' was being chased for long
distances by hundreds of them in Venezuela.
