interested in structural changes and Solidarity. ... If there is
pluralism and Solidarity, those people who refused to accept
government posts will have an open road.'' _-_ Solidarity leader
Lech Walesa, saying the opposition's acceptance of government posts
that have been offered depends on whether the government could
bring about change and accept the banned union.
