investigated for violating a federal law against selling illegal
drugs within 1,000 feet of a school. The charge carries a minimum
sentence of one year in prison and a maximum of 40 years.
   Other cases will be investigated by the district attorney, he
said. He estimated that a third of the suspects are gang members.
   The officers went to schools in the downtown, Wilmington,
Sepulveda, Pacoima, El Sereno, Hyde Park and South-Central areas.
