</TEXT>
<DATELINE>RALEIGH, N.C. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Two Tuscarora Indians who staged an armed
takeover of a newspaper office and held hostages for 10 hours, in
what they said was a protest of local corruption, were found
innocent of all charges Friday.
</TEXT>
